{"tid":2413600,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"緣份．占卜塔羅測半年運勢～","createTime":"2021-02-18T23:42:37.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-14T16:34:37.000Z","uid":285877,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":140,"replies":[{"pid":"dbade5f26a15c447b94851c2699dc74d1c6ce8d8","tid":2413600,"uid":285877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T23:42:37.000Z","msg":"第一次出post，多多支持<br />\n講少少背景先：<br />\n學左幾年，有幫人占卜開<br />\n今次免費幫大家占一條問題測半年走勢<br />\n亦會透過今次教大家如何發問問題能夠精準有效😉<br />\n<br />\n自己都有幫人做身、心、靈治療<br />\n皆因2019-去年患左情緒病，唔想成日食藥，開始接觸下一啲身心靈課程。今年年頭終於唔洗見醫生啦✌🏼 <br />\n<br />\n我一切隨緣隨心，同埋真心幫人，如果想測下運程，或者想了解一下身心靈一啲資訊都可以留低tg ，等我搵你。"},{"pid":"77d78130532517a4d46f85422638a09ca8f11b4a","tid":2413600,"uid":55458,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T23:43:42.000Z","msg":"卜下我幾時食到靚女<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7016f8f9c2b2baac38c72f88e20227285e09a277","tid":2413600,"uid":285877,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"77d78130532517a4d46f85422638a09ca8f11b4a","tid":2413600,"uid":55458,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T23:43:42.000Z","msg":"卜下我幾時食到靚女<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T23:45:45.000Z","msg":"☺️留低tg 睇吓我幫唔幫你搵到"},{"pid":"d01a205b8c0701641bb8ce2b580c6c35739ffa9e","tid":2413600,"uid":39215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T23:50:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b01c6feeaa37811401aafa73e489cab6bf1bfa5c","tid":2413600,"uid":150675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T23:51:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />